	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p>Throat Punch is a @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.hW3DmOPgBpa7lGU8]{Precision Attacks}.</p><p><strong>Alternative Melee Sneak Attack</strong> - 1 Creature - 1 Round</p><p>You can sacrifice [[/r 1d6]] of your @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.8Ctt1vOsZuKXxAIN]{sneak attack} damage to interrupt and briefly prevent your opponent from speaking. You can use this option with <strong>melee attacks only</strong> .</p><p><strong>[[/save constitution]]{Constitution Save}</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.8Ctt1vOsZuKXxAIN]{Sneak Attack} (-1d6) bludgeoning damage. Target is &amp;Reference[silenced].</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.8Ctt1vOsZuKXxAIN]{Sneak Attack} (-1d6) bludgeoning damage.</p></li></ul>",
